claim.claim-text:
A modified factor VII (FVII) polypeptide, comprising a modification in a FVII polypeptide, wherein:
the polypeptide comprises a modification that is an amino acid replacement at a position corresponding to position 286 in a FVII polypeptide having the sequence of amino acids set forth in SEQ ID NO:3 or in a corresponding residue in a FVII polypeptide;
the amino acid replacement is Gln (Q) with Arg (R);
the replacement at position 286 results in a modified FVII polypeptide that exhibits increased coagulant activity compared to the FVII polypeptide that does not have the modification at position 286; and
the polypeptide comprises only 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 or 7 amino acid modifications compared to the unmodified polypeptide and optionally a heterologous Gla domain or a portion thereof.
